        <item>
            <title>【評測】Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 輕巧天涯鏡，人像實試 + 微距出色</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/18/sony-fe-24-50mm-f2-8-g-review/dc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sony-fe-24-50mm-f2-8-g-review</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/18/sony-fe-24-50mm-f2-8-g-review/dc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 12:42:24 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[數碼相機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[相機測試]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[24-50mm]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[鏡頭]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1225016</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>以往 f/2.8 大光圈變焦鏡頭，例如大三元鏡頭 f/2.8 16-35mm, 24-70mm, 70-200mm 都是好多攝影愛好者的目標。始終光圈夠大，在夜晚拍攝雜訊會少得多，而且能製造迷人散景效果。今次 Sony 提出了一個超強性價比的全新 f/2.8 大光圈選擇，就是這次介紹的 Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G。它的焦段比較特別，但重點是價格相宜、輕巧設計，同時兼備相當不錯的性能。當然這種平靚正的鏡頭，用上手還是會感到有少許限制，是否容許這些限制，成為你入手這支性價比超強鏡頭的最後考慮。以下小編就同 unwire 記者 Keiko 一齊到公園試用此鏡。分析這鏡頭的特點與分享使用感受。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225098" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09275-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09275-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09275.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><a title="DSC08904" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/53595588890/in/album-72177720315512572/" data-flickr-embed="true" data-header="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53595588890_7e539abba5_c.jpg" alt="DSC08904" width="800" height="533" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲以下所有試相，點擊圖片後可進入 Flickr 相簿放大閲覽</p><p>＞＞＞<a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/albums/72177720315512572/">點擊進入 Flickr 相簿可看所有試相</a>＜＜＜</p><h2>光學性能與定位</h2><p>這支鏡頭屬於著重性價比的 Sony G 鏡頭系列，同 G Master 系列作一個區隔。但單從光圈等規格、性能上，它絕不會比 GM 鏡頭差得多。就光學性能來説，它在 24-70mm G Master 第一代和 G Master 第二代之間，但就提供體積更小的鏡身，重量也只有 440 克。今時今日的用家已追求輕便實用，A7C 系列大賣就是最好證明，而這支鏡頭也非常適合 A7C 系列機身。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225111" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09242-694x467.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="467" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09242-694x467.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09242.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225100" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09286-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09286-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09286.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225101" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09287-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09287-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09287.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 最長焦距只是去到 50mm，但對於好多朋友去旅行、平時街拍，50mm 已經非常夠用。要考慮到它的輕細鏡身與只是 GM 鏡頭一半的價格，可説是合理的等價交換。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225102" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09267-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09267-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09267.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225108" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09294-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09294-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09294.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲A7CR 配合附加手柄後，用上此鏡剛剛好</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225109" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09295-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09295-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09295.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲A7CR 就算沒有加手柄，機身與鏡頭比例也是很不錯</p><p>以相片拍攝的成像清晰度來説，Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 無論在 24mm 至到 50mm 都能拍出令人滿意的相片。在全開光圈時的成像鋭利度與對比度都非常不錯，能夠與第一代 G Master 鏡頭媲美。而在人像拍攝時產生的背景淺景深效果，也緊貼了 GM 鏡頭的水準。當然需要極致柔滑散景，你還得嘗試一下第二代 GM 鏡頭，但在 G 鏡上所得的相片已經很滿意。</p><p><a title="DSC08912" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/53595345223/in/album-72177720315512572/" data-flickr-embed="true" data-header="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53595345223_24d816760a_c.jpg" alt="DSC08912" width="800" height="533" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC08945" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/53595457064/in/album-72177720315512572/" data-flickr-embed="true" data-header="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53595457064_0d08c403c0_c.jpg" alt="DSC08945" width="800" height="533" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲相片經過顏色後製處理</p><p><a title="DSC08968" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/53595345018/in/album-72177720315512572/" data-flickr-embed="true" data-header="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53595345018_58b4defaea_c.jpg" alt="DSC08968" width="800" height="533" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC09002" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/53594263322/in/album-72177720315512572/" data-flickr-embed="true" data-header="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53594263322_01e36ef7e5_c.jpg" alt="DSC09002" width="800" height="533" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲相片經過顏色後製處理</p><h2>為何 24-50mm 已經夠用</h2><p>Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 規格上同 24-70mm F2.8 GM 對比，最明顯就只有缺乏了 51-70mm 的方面的焦段，但這焦段通常用來實現人物、景物的特寫。而事實上在此鏡頭中，你已經擁有 24mm、28mm、35mm 以及 50mm 這幾個常用焦段，有關特寫的拍攝，亦可用「人肉」變焦自己走近一點便可（撇除壓縮感等因素）。24-50mm 這個焦段已相當夠用，絕對是一支適合旅遊、日常影相拍 vlog、影食飯的「天涯鏡」。</p><p>24mm：私房人像近攝、廣闊風景照</p><p>28mm：較繁忙街道的街拍、風景照、人物 + 風景照</p><p>35mm：較闊街道的街拍、風景照、人像相片、人物 + 風景照</p><p>50mm：街拍中突顯街中某單一人物或事物、具有迷人景深的人像相片</p><p><a title="DSC08940" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/53595457109/in/album-72177720315512572/" data-flickr-embed="true" data-header="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53595457109_322580a401_c.jpg" alt="DSC08940" width="533" height="800" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲約 35mm（人物加景物）</p><p><a title="DSC08996" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/53595588290/in/album-72177720315512572/" data-flickr-embed="true" data-header="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53595588290_52f52873c5_c.jpg" alt="DSC08996" width="800" height="533" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲約 40mm（人物加景物）相片經過顏色後製處理</p><p><a title="DSC09005" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/53594263292/in/album-72177720315512572/" data-flickr-embed="true" data-header="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53594263292_feab49032f_c.jpg" alt="DSC09005" width="800" height="533" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲50mm（人物）顏色經過後製處理</p><p><a title="DSC08977" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/53594263852/in/album-72177720315512572/" data-flickr-embed="true" data-header="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53594263852_e2fbea42b0_c.jpg" alt="DSC08977" width="533" height="800" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC09202" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/53595344473/in/album-72177720315512572/" data-flickr-embed="true" data-header="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53595344473_bfe378c54f_c.jpg" alt="DSC09202" width="800" height="533" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC09203" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/53595137091/in/album-72177720315512572/" data-flickr-embed="true" data-header="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53595137091_77628eb4b0_c.jpg" alt="DSC09203" width="800" height="533" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/21/sony-fe-24-50mm-f2-8-g/dc/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【現場評測】Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 現埸實試　新焦段+輕巧+畫質媲美第一代 G Master</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>鏡身在 50mm 焦段縮到最短，便利人像攝影用家<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></h2><p>一般鏡頭包括 GM 那款 24-70mm f/2.8 鏡頭，其外變焦設計是在最廣角端如 24mm 收起所有鏡片到鏡筒，在使用 35mm、50mm 時部份鏡片才會從鏡筒中突起。今次 Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 卻相反在 50mm 焦段時就把所有鏡片收起於鏡筒內，反倒是在鏡頭變 wide 時才會把鏡筒伸出。這種設計很適合基本用於人像攝影的用家，在使用 50mm 拍攝時鏡筒收到最緊致，就算是 35mm 鏡筒都只是略為突起。</p><p>50mm 至到 24mm 的鏡筒伸出狀況：</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225104" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09274-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09274-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09274.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲50mm</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225105" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09273-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09273-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09273.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲35mm</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225106" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09272-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09272-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09272.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲28mm</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225107" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09271-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09271-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09271.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲24mm</p><h2>對焦性能不下於 GM 鏡頭</h2><p>Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 裝備有兩個線性自動對焦馬達，能夠與高速連拍相機如 A9 III 配合使用，達到每秒 120 幀的對焦追蹤。即使在今次試用的 A7CR 高像素相機中，仍可保持高速而準確的連續對焦。感覺上鏡頭對焦速度已同 GM 鏡頭相當接近。尤其是人像拍攝，捕捉眼睛的準確度、速度都極高，就算被攝者轉身，也能快速切換至人物驅體偵測，不會突然迷焦。當人物轉身返回正面，對焦可重回被攝者眼睛上，整個過程都是極為順滑的。</p><p><a title="DSC08927" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/53595588815/in/album-72177720315512572/" data-flickr-embed="true" data-header="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53595588815_4495c33603_c.jpg" alt="DSC08927" width="800" height="533" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲只要鏡頭內有人物，相機＋鏡頭可高速對焦人物眼睛、臉部、驅體</p><h2>小心畸邊控制</h2><p>不過此鏡最需要的，就是配合機身內置的鏡頭補正功能。鏡頭整體來説在機身修正之下，畸變現象幾乎消失。但如果關閉修正功能，在 24mm 焦段出現的桶型畸變會較為明顯，即使在 50mm 焦段仍會有一點點畸變現象發生，這會令到人像攝影中被攝者臉部肌肉看上去會更加厚。無論如何，這次小編與 Keiko 合作的人像相片測試中，未有發現明顯臉部變肥的情況。</p><p><a title="DSC08924" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/53594263702/in/album-72177720315512572/" data-flickr-embed="true" data-header="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53594263702_de2b39a375_c.jpg" alt="DSC08924" width="800" height="533" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2>近攝都無問題</h2><p>在 24mm 焦段時 Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 的最近對焦距離為 0.19 米、在 50mm 焦段時最近對焦距離 0.3 米，最大放大倍率為 0.3x。雖然未有 GM 鏡那般強橫，但也完全在實用領域。在旅行時用來拍攝食物、小擺設，它都能夠應付自如。突顯到 Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 是一支全能的天涯鏡。</p><p><a title="DSC08987" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/53595456714/in/album-72177720315512572/" data-flickr-embed="true" data-header="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53595456714_75985cc981_c.jpg" alt="DSC08987" width="800" height="533" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲相片經過顏色後製處理</p><p>除了線性馬達，在其他功能方面 Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 都與 GM 鏡頭十分類似，例如有齊可無段變換、逐格變換的光圈環、可自訂功能的操作按鈕、可抵受微雨的密封設計等。鏡頭配備的花形遮光罩在實際用途之外，也令到整副裝備看上去十分專業。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225103" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09260-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09260-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09260.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/21/sony-fe-24-50mm-f2-8-g/dc/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【現場評測】Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 現埸實試　新焦段+輕巧+畫質媲美第一代 G Master</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>總結：高性價比大光圈天涯鏡</h2><p>Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 的官方建議零售價是 HK$8,990，是另一支更高階 GM 鏡頭 Sony FE 24-70mm F2.8 GM II 價格 HK$17,990 的一半，價格因素可謂不容忽視。在大家都好渴望需要一支大光圈鏡頭，而 Sony 現在有一支涵蓋 24mm 至到 50mm 焦段的鏡頭面世，不吸引才是假的。此鏡頭為用户提供了一個經濟實惠的選擇，特別是對於那些不需要 70mm 長焦端，但希望保持良好畫質和輕巧設計的攝影師來説，Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 絕對是高性價比的選擇。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225110" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09244-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09244-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kan09244.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/21/sony-fe-24-50mm-f2-8-g/dc/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【現場評測】Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 現埸實試　新焦段+輕巧+畫質媲美第一代 G Master</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/18/sony-fe-24-50mm-f2-8-g-review/dc/">【評測】Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 輕巧天涯鏡，人像實試 + 微距出色</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
